snippet.title: Surviving the Aftermath: New Alliances - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Become the Leader of the surviving societies in Surviving the Aftermath: New Alliances. The future of humanity is in your hands: find allies, fight common enemies, and unite the Wasteland!

Surviving the Aftermath: New Alliances will release on June 16 on PC, wishlist it now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1803780/Surviving_the_Aftermath_New_Alliances

Paradox on YouTube:
---------------------------
ParadoxInteractive - http://youtube.com/ParadoxInteractive
Trailers, Feature Breakdowns, Dev Diaries, and more.

Paradox Grand Strategy - http://youtube.com/ParadoxGrandStrategy
Gameplay of our Historical Grand Strategy Games: CK3, EU4, and HOI4.

The Official Stellaris YouTube channel - https://www.youtube.com/c/StellarisOfficial
Join us as we interact with diverse alien species and discover strange new worlds.
